title.rendered: List of Qualified Candidates for Community Nursing – 2021 Intake

content.rendered: The under-listed candidates are QUALIFIED to write the Entrance Examination into COMMUNITY Nursing Programme scheduled for Saturday 24th July, 2021. All shortlisted candidates are to come along with their Acknowledgement Cards and Letter of Identification of Residence to their Exam Venues. Candidates should check their names and Classrooms/Halls where they will sit for their exams. No candidate will be allowed to sit for the exams where he/she is not assigned to.
